          "language": "py",
          "contents": "def play_hype_song():\n  # Plays a high-energy song to get you pumped up\n  print(\"Playing hype song: 'Let's Go!'\")\n\ndef play_chill_song():\n  # Plays a calm song to help you relax while getting ready\n  print(\"Playing chill song: 'Easy Morning'\")\n\ndef morning_playlist():\n  play_hype_song\n  play_chill_sng()\n\nmorning_playlist()\n",
